description:
"mellow" is the 8th song off my new beattape "souls" releaseing August 27, 2021. mellow takes my usual style and throws it out the window. i could listen to this on reapeat over and over. just sounds so pleasing to my ear. 

the cover art was generated by AI using the text prompt "mellow souls." nothing more mellow than sitting on the beach, watching the sunset. 

Bop your head and enjoy the music. If you purchase this piece, hit me up on twitter @ryanartwalker and I will send you the album with high quality AIFF files!
